query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `departments` (
  `id` int NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `description` text,
  `createdAt` datetime DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
);
